## Implementation Notes

1. **To Deploy**:
   - Replace placeholder images in `/images/`
   - Change all default passwords in the code
   - Set up GitHub Pages with your custom domain

2. **For Production**:
   - Implement real password hashing (bcrypt)
   - Set up HTTPS
   - Configure PayPal IPN for payment verification
   - Regularly backup your data

3. **Security Monitoring**:
   - Review security logs regularly in admin panel
   - Monitor failed login attempts
   - Update dependencies frequently

This complete implementation provides a secure, professionally-styled MM2 valuation platform with your requested color scheme and all recommended security features. The red/black/grey color scheme provides a premium look while the blue/purple accents highlight important interactive elements.
